tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RetinaScans (
    scan_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    employee_id INT,
    scan_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    scan_result BOOLEAN NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (employee_id) REFERENCES Employee(employee_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Employee (
  employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(50),
  position VARCHAR(50),
  department VARCHAR(50),
  retina_scan_data VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE AccessLog (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_id INT,
  access_time TIMESTAMP,
  access_location VARCHAR(100),
  FOREIGN KEY (employee_id) REFERENCES Employee(employee_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AreaAccess (
  access_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_id INT,
  area_id INT,
  access_time TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (employee_id) REFERENCES Employee(employee_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (area_id) REFERENCES SecureArea(area_id)
);

CREATE TABLE RetinaData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_id INT,
  retina_scan_data VARCHAR(100),
  scan_time TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (employee_id) REFERENCES Employee(employee_id)
);
